<p><a href="http://www.webstuffshare.com/2012/03/creating-consecutive-slide-using-jquery/" title="Creating Consecutive Slide Using jQuery"><img src="http://farm4.staticflickr.com/3706/8909728665_6d433d89dd_z.jpg" width="640" height="106" alt="Creating Consecutive Slide Using jQuery"></a></p>

