  </script>
  <script type="text/javascript"
          src="http://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/show_ads.js">
  </script>
</div></p>

<h2>Quovolverのデモ</h2>

<p>jQueyr プラグイン Quovolverってどんなの？ということ下はDemoページのリンクです。</p>

<p><a href="http://sebnitu.github.io/Quovolver/" title="jQueyr プラグイン Quovolver"><img src="http://farm3.staticflickr.com/2850/8909304861_9f6310b1c5_z.jpg" width="640" height="201" alt="jQueyr プラグイン Quovolver"></a></p>

<p>Webページ内の特定のHTML要素が変化していくので、目立たせたい場所には持って来いですね！</p>

<h2>サンプルソース</h2>

<p>導入もシンプルです。まずはこちらからファイルをダウンロード。</p>

<p><strong><a href="https://github.com/sebnitu/Quovolver">sebnitu/Quovolver · GitHub</a></strong></p>

<p>HTMLにjavascriptを宣言。</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
<span class='line-number'>8</span>
<span class='line-number'>9</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;script </span><span class="na">src=</span><span class="s">&quot;http://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/1.7.1/jquery.min.js&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;script </span><span class="na">src=</span><span class="s">&quot;jquery.quovolver.js&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;&lt;/script&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;p&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div></p>

<p>同じくHTML側に変化させる要素を設置。</p>

<p><div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
<span class='line-number'>4</span>
<span class='line-number'>5</span>
<span class='line-number'>6</span>
<span class='line-number'>7</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='html'><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;/p&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;ul</span> <span class="na">class=</span><span class="s">&quot;quotes&quot;</span><span class="nt">&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="nt">&lt;li&gt;</span>hoge<span class="nt">&lt;/li&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="nt">&lt;li&gt;</span>fuga<span class="nt">&lt;/li&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'>    <span class="nt">&lt;li&gt;</span>moge<span class="nt">&lt;/li&gt;</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="nt">&lt;/div&gt;</span><span class="c">&lt;!-- .quotes --&gt;</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

あとはjavascript側に下の要素を設置でコーディングは完了。

<div class='bogus-wrapper'><notextile><figure class='code'> <div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class='line-number'>1</span>
<span class='line-number'>2</span>
<span class='line-number'>3</span>
</pre></td><td class='code'><pre><code class='javascript'><span class='line'><span class="nx">$</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">document</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="nx">ready</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="kd">function</span><span class="p">()</span> <span class="p">{</span>
</span><span class='line'>  <span class="nx">$</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">&#39;ul.quotes&#39;</span><span class="p">).</span><span class="nx">quovolver</span><span class="p">();</span>
</span><span class='line'><span class="p">});</span>
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

アニメーションのON/OFFや、切り替え時間(秒)の変更などもオプションで変更できます。<br/>詳しくは下の公式サイトを御覧ください。

